plot: If your mistakes lead to your death, how can you learn from them?

In a dark alley after an ambush, Ray gets beaten up accompanying sale of guns. He quickly realizes his contact set him up, takes him hostage and has the robbers return the guns before he releases his hostage. Being greedy robbers, they try again to rip him off, not realizing Ray's been around the block before, and it doesn't end well for them. However, Ray is sometimes his worst enemy and ends up in jail for something completely avoidable.
